m-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black-12.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black-12.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black-12.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black-12.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img width=\"2500\" height=\"1667\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-6-von-19.jpg?fit=1200,1667&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-6-von-19.jpg?w=2500&amp;quality=75 2500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-6-von-19.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-6-von-19.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-6-von-19.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-6-von-19.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-6-von-19.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>Thanks to its rigid construction, the Grill Bag is ready for the rough stuff without the need for a decaleur. The expanded 12-liter capacity is optimized for bikepacking and long-distance cycling, yet with the included shoulder carry strap it‘s equally at home on and off the bike in the city.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2500\" height=\"1667\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black-9.jpg?fit=1200,1667&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black-9.jpg?w=2500&amp;quality=75 2500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black-9.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black-9.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black-9.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black-9.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black-9.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2500\" height=\"1667\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black.jpg?fit=1200,1667&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black.jpg?w=2500&amp;quality=75 2500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2500\" height=\"1667\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black-2.jpg?fit=1200,1667&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black-2.jpg?w=2500&amp;quality=75 2500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black-2.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black-2.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black-2.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black-2.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-Grill-Bag-RX36-black-2.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>The Grill Bag features the same innovative „origami“ folding lid and no-fuss universal mounting of the original Diamond Bag using FidLock hardware. The construction is highly weather-resistant and features two internal mesh pockets. The Grill Bag‘s unique angular design reduces interference with drop-bar shifters compared to traditional setups.</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2500\" height=\"1667\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-19-von-19.jpg?fit=1200,1667&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-19-von-19.jpg?w=2500&amp;quality=75 2500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-19-von-19.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-19-von-19.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-19-von-19.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-19-von-19.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-19-von-19.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2500\" height=\"1667\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-15-von-19.jpg?fit=1200,1667&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-15-von-19.jpg?w=2500&amp;quality=75 2500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-15-von-19.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-15-von-19.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-15-von-19.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-15-von-19.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-15-von-19.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"2500\" height=\"1667\" src=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-1-von-4.jpg?fit=1200,1667&amp;quality=75\" srcset=\"https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-1-von-4.jpg?w=2500&amp;quality=75 2500w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-1-von-4.jpg?resize=1200,800&amp;quality=75 1200w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-1-von-4.jpg?resize=2000,1334&amp;quality=75 2000w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-1-von-4.jpg?resize=768,512&amp;quality=75 768w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-1-von-4.jpg?resize=1536,1024&amp;quality=75 1536w, https://media.theradavist.com/uploads/2024/03/gramm-tourpacking-MAREN-Custom-Frame-Bag-1-von-4.jpg?resize=2048,1366&amp;quality=75 2048w\" /></p>\n<p>The Grill Bag is available now in Dimension Polyant X-Pac RX36 Black (100% post-consumer recycled polyester) and ECOPAK Ultra X 200 Black Magic. Both variants feature a light-colored ECOPAK 200 Silver Bullet liner and a tough Hypalon base. Like the Diamond Bag, the Grill Bag is handmade in small batches by our manufacturing partner in Portugal.</p>\n<p><strong>Specs:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>12 liters capacity</li>\n<li>Width 190-220 mm, height 290-300 mm, depth 210 mm</li>\n<li>Weight 735 g (ECOPAKUltra) / 820 g (X-PacRX36)</li>\n<li>Cost €269 / 289 for bag only or €409 / 429 bundled with Allygn Components Grill Rack</li>\n</ul>\n<p>See more at <a href=\"https://www.gramm-tourpacking.com/shopnow/grill-bag\" target=\"_blank\">Gramm Tourpacking</a>.</p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://theradavist.com/gramm-tourpacking-grill-bag/\">Gramm Tourpacking Grill Bag</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://theradavist.com\">The Radavist</a>.</p>","author":"John Watson","siteTitle":"The Radavist","siteHash":"96eb481d8084f04a4602bac57874ba717baf56b758f45547b5caf2312da766ef","entryHash":"ca1701b8a33fda70cdef431146095a3538b86425035c50d63306e6c7f90a5262","category":"Cycling"}